@Node "Archive@§0"

The Close Button

This Button iconifies Archive. To quit Archive, use Project/Quit Archive.

Note:
To quit Archive when clicking the close button, see
@{"ToolTypes" Link "Archive@Startup"}.
@EndNode

@Node "Archive@§1"

The CD Selection Field

Here you can select the title of a catalogized CD.
The title is then displayed in the field below. There you can edit the
title.
@EndNode

@Node "Archive@§2"

The Track Selection Field

Here you can select a track title a selected CD.
The title is then displayed in the field below. There you can edit the
title.
@EndNode

@Node "Archive@§3"

The CD Name Editing Field

Here you can edit the title of a selected CD.

Note 1:
Finish editing by pressing the return key!

Note 2:
Edited catalogs will be automatically saved.
@EndNode

@Node "Archive@§4"

The Track Title Editing Field

Here you can edit the title of the selected track of the selected CD.

Note 1:
Finish editing by pressing the return key!

Note 2:
Edited catalogs will be automatically saved.

@EndNode

